{"tid":376764,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲散左好多年都忘記唔到個ex","createTime":"2017-08-27T08:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T14:24:59.000Z","uid":81018,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dc8d94781c3ce3253a050453b47df3edfb5e1bc0","tid":376764,"uid":81018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:32:45.000Z","msg":"我同我個ex散左好多年 但係到今日都係忘記唔到佢 咁多年我唔係無拍過拖 但係好快就同個女仔講散 原因係唔想一個愛我嘅人 浪費佢心機係一個一定唔會愛佢嘅人 咁多年黎 唔係無心動過 但係個感覺同個ex比我嘅感覺好唔同 同個ex嘅感覺係見到佢笑 自己都會好開心 但其他人比自己嘅感覺就只係一秒嘅心動 到宜家直情同女仔fd單獨出完街番到屋企係到唱閉起雙眼我最掛念誰 眼睛張開身邊竟是誰  我係咪呢世都忘記唔到個ex呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd4b4b7404c7c949766cce43c5072a397ecad44","tid":376764,"uid":109768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:34:00.000Z","msg":"散左幾耐？<br />\n為咩散？"},{"pid":"2dd26d0855130a1f68b74a2c2b2ac659500f452f","tid":376764,"uid":140379,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:36:39.000Z","msg":"會懷念 會掛住 永遠係心目中都會留一個位置比佢 但留住既係回憶 吾係愛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6fe7ec1d6fe294234ff641e8931be9580c870a","tid":376764,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:40:25.000Z","msg":"3年了。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945d2027ffa8306a79cf0ee6095ae65dd6bb2f40","tid":376764,"uid":81018,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>散左幾耐？<br />\n為咩散？</blockquote><br />\n散左4年了 因為我日日發佢脾氣 我脾氣勁臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078251ef9690b4b6e4da6f0b9e7c2385ae23edef","tid":376764,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:43:12.000Z","msg":"兩年"},{"pid":"623638536a48d5590d5f6e1141b8a41255782508","tid":376764,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:43:18.000Z","msg":"6年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agr